    <h2><code>IF ELSE</code> statement</h2>
	<p>The IF ELSE statement can be used as a main statement, or within a parent statement, to return a value depending on whether a condition, or a series of conditions match. The statement allows for multiple <code>ELSE IF</code> expressions, and a final <code>ELSE</code> expression, with no limit to the number of <code>ELSE IF</code> conditional expressions.</p>
